          <a href="https://github.com/dholliday3/coros-training-mcp/blob/main/README.md">Docs</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="fine disclaimer">
        Uses the unofficial COROS Training Hub API. Not affiliated with or endorsed by COROS.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="copy.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
